translate portuguese welch9_77b3956a:

    # "In Ms. Welch's class, I try to focus on my test, attempting to recall all the information that I had memorized while studying earlier in the week."
    "Na aula da Sra. Welch, tento concentrar-me no meu teste, tentando recordar toda a informação que tinha memorizado enquanto estudava no início da semana."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:13
translate portuguese welch9_1d38c971:

    # "Ms. Welch walks through the class, looking to see how everybody is doing and watching out for any cheaters."
    "A Sra. Welch percorre a sala, a ver como está a correr tudo e atenta a eventuais batoteiros."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:16
translate portuguese welch9_92d9ffe5:

    # "When she passes by my desk, she slides a small note down in front of me."
    "Quando passa pela minha secretária, desliza um pequeno bilhete à minha frente."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:17
translate portuguese welch9_67c479b9:

    # "She does it so slyly, not even looking down as she places it, never missing a step as she continues walking the room."
    "Fá-lo de forma tão discreta, sem sequer baixar o olhar ao colocá-lo, sem perder o ritmo enquanto continua a percorrer a sala."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:18
translate portuguese welch9_0e4d4622:

    # "I quietly unfold the note and take a look."
    "Desdobro silenciosamente o bilhete e dou uma olhadela."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:25
translate portuguese welch9_95ec0fac:

    # "I look up again and see her standing by her desk, smiling at me."
    "Olho para cima novamente e vejo-a de pé junto à sua secretária, a sorrir para mim."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:26
translate portuguese welch9_00e23a96:

    # "She wants to talk to me. And gave me her phone number."
    "Ela quer falar comigo. E deu-me o seu número de telefone."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:27
translate portuguese welch9_6bf4ecfb:

    # "I'll have to give her a call sometime soon, I guess."
    "Vou ter de lhe ligar em breve, acho eu."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:30
